These are Puzzles for 1x7 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-1::.
There are 7 different nationalities: russian, american, french, dutch, malaysian, japanese, egyptian
 1. the russian is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5
 2. the dutch is somewhere between the japanese and the malaysian##7
 3. the american is somewhere between the japanese and the russian##7
 4. the american is somewhere to the left of the french##5
 5. the egyptian is not to the left of the japanese##8
 6. the american is in an odd position##4
 7. the japanese is on the left or right of the dutch##3
 8. the japanese is somewhere between the malaysian and the egyptian##7
 9. the french is not to the right of the dutch##8
10. the russian is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |  5   |  6  |   7    |
| Nationality   | malaysian | russian | american | french | dutch | japanese | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-2::.
House: futuristic, art-deco, modern, tower, cottage, townhouse, palace
 1. the townhouse house is the townhouse house##1
 2. the modern house is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
 3. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5
 4. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
 5. the townhouse house is on the left or right of the palace house##3
 6. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the art-deco house##5
 7. the futuristic house is on the left of the cottage house##1
 8. the townhouse house is on the left of the palace house##1
 9. the palace house is in an even position##4
10. the cottage house is not to the left of the futuristic house##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |       5       |    6     |      7       |
| House   | tower | art-deco | townhouse | palace | modern | futuristic | cottage |

