.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-3::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, martial-arts, zombie, documentary, spy, romance, disaster
 1. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the person watching romance movies##8
 2. the person watching disaster movies is in an even position##4
 3. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##5
 4. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left or right of the person watching romance movies##3
 6. the person watching disaster movies is not to the right of the person watching western movies##8
 7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere between the person watching romance movies and the person watching martial-arts movies##7
 8. the person watching western movies is in an odd position##4
 9. the person watching western movies is not to the right of the person watching zombie movies##8
10. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |      4      |   5   |    6    |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | romance | documentary | disaster | western | zombie | martial-arts |

