.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-4::.
There 7 different types of food: asparagus, grapefruit, watermelon, garlic, onion, plum, pepper
 1. the person eating asparagus is somewhere between the person eating watermelon and the person eating grapefruit##7
 2. the person eating plum is somewhere to the right of the person eating grapefruit##5
 3. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating plum##1
 4. the person eating onion is somewhere between the person eating pepper and the person eating grapefruit##7
 5. the person eating pepper is somewhere between the person eating onion and the person eating garlic##7
 6. the person eating garlic is somewhere between the person eating asparagus and the person eating pepper##7
 7. the person eating asparagus is not to the right of the person eating plum##8
 8. the person eating garlic is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3
 9. the person eating pepper is not to the left of the person eating garlic##8
10. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |  2  |   3   |    4     |   5   |   6    |  7   |
| Food   | watermelon | asparagus | garlic | pepper | onion | grapefruit | plum |

