6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of techno##1
7. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
8. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
9. the fan of soul is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |    4     |   5    |   6   |    7     |
| Music-Genre   | soul | dubstep | ambient | r&b | hip-hop | techno | punk |

