 2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere between the person who's hobby is hiking and the person who's hobby is filmmaking##7
 4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 5. the person who's hobby is collecting is not to the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
 6. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 8. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
 9. the person who's hobby is fishing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##5
10. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |    4    |    5     |    6    |     7     |
| Hobby   | collecting | hiking | fishing | video-games | rock-climbing | chess | filmmaking |

