 1. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5
 2. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 3. the owner of the frog is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is not to the right of the owner of the dog##8
 5. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the frog##5
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the frog##5
 7. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
 8. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the frog and the owner of the goldfish##2
 9. the owner of the fish is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
10. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the owner of the cat##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |   3    |   4    |     5     |    6     |     7     |
| Pet   | cat | guinea-pig | dog | fish | frog | rat | goldfish |

