6. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere between the person traveling to colone and the person traveling to boston##7
8. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to colone##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |   5   |    6    |    7    |
