.:: Puzzle 1x7-Level-8-14::.
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: november, january, september, april, july, june, august
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in august is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
 3. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in january and the person who's birthday is in june##7
 4. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in august##7
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
 6. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5
10. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
11. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |  2   |    3    |   4    |  5   |  6   |   7   |
| Birthday   | june | july | september | august | january | april | november |

