 6. the designer is somewhere to the left of the journalist##5
 7. the architect is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
 8. the videographer is not to the left of the engineer##8
 9. the videographer is somewhere between the lawyer and the firefighter##7
10. the videographer is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
11. the engineer is on the left or right of the designer##3
12. the designer is on the right of the architect##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |    3    |    4     |     5      |     6     |     7      |
| Job   | firefighter | architect | designer | engineer | journalist | videographer | lawyer |

